data.name: label4.Text
data.value: TIPS: • This program is free and open-source. If you paid for it, you got scammed. • It is highly recommended to connect your cars batter to a charger while flashing! • Please use a fully charged laptop (or plugged in) and don't allow it to sleep or turn off! • Reading takes approximately 30 minutes. • Flashing takes approximately 2 minutes. • Checksum will be corrected automatically if necessary. • When flashing starts, the car will shut down. It will wake up when flashing is complete. • Do not attempt to flash someone else's bin unless you are SURE you know what you're doing!
